/>\n<br />\n好似打機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T17:26:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:51:28.000Z","msg":"軍事電競<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f09a0007fdda13e950c26be85814acb125dd87","tid":1004733,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:01:17.000Z","msg":"美國海軍原初計劃建32艘朱瓦特級驅逐艦，但因新實驗性技術成本過高，建造數量一減再減，最終計劃只建造3艘朱瓦特級，分別為DDG-1000、DDG-1001與DDG-1002<br />\n<br />\nCut咁多艘"},{"pid":"9083af43027dda78bef3e0d02d2719aafc04df62","tid":1004733,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7f09a0007fdda13e950c26be85814acb125dd87","tid":1004733,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:01:17.000Z","msg":"美國海軍原初計劃建32艘朱瓦特級驅逐艦，但因新實驗性技術成本過高，建造數量一減再減，最終計劃只建造3艘朱瓦特級，分別為DDG-1000、DDG-1001與DDG-1002<br />\n<br />\nCut咁多艘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"destroyer本身都唔需要咁多<br />\n就算現役都好撚屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}